{"tid":224524,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係死神，專門審判自殺嘅人","createTime":"2017-05-01T06:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T07:08:40.000Z","uid":108643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"40b4ec1793d3e52fcfaf49c22f89988f2dfe55e2","tid":224524,"uid":108643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T06:38:25.000Z","msg":"我係死神。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對於我嘅存在係點嘅一回事，我從來冇特別去深究。因為我天職，係去審判自殺而死嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所謂「審判」，就係睇下佢哋因為啲乜自殺。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可笑嘅係， 人類隨住生活質素變得越好，自殺嘅情況就越多，令我覺得好奇且奇怪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以兩日之前，我離開咗地獄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上去人界，親自去接觸即將自殺之人。"},{"pid":"1edf20e1ba45d3f68c5367a6d97b7e258c82097f","tid":224524,"uid":111771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T06:39:22.000Z","msg":"完"},{"pid":"b357f9d4615b6848074c5ea10ccac0d1a8d00697","tid":224524,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T06:44:57.000Z","msg":"wrong<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"354987785227b927fa96d7ee94f6b73856f969b8","tid":224524,"uid":43367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T07:08:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}